@startuml
title Sistema de supervision sanitaria para vendedores de ceviche de pota - Arquitectura fisica en nube

skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam nodeStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Usuario final\nCiudadano / Vendedor /\nInspector / Administrador" as Usuario
actor "Equipo de desarrollo" as Dev

cloud "Internet" as Internet

node "GitHub" as GitHub {
  artifact "Repositorio\nmain / develop / feature" as Repo
}

node "GitHub Actions" as GHA {
  component "Pipeline CI/CD\nbuild + test + deploy" as Pipeline
}

cloud "Vercel" as Vercel {
  node "Vercel Edge Network / CDN" as CDN
  node "Vercel Hosting" as Hosting {
    artifact "Aplicacion Next.js" as NextApp
  }
  node "Vercel Serverless Functions" as Functions {
    component "API / server-side functions" as ServerlessAPI
  }
  component "Vercel Logs\nAnalytics" as VercelLogs
}

cloud "Supabase" as Supabase {
  component "Supabase Auth" as SupabaseAuth
  database "Supabase PostgreSQL" as SupabaseDB
  folder "Supabase Storage" as SupabaseStorage
  component "Supabase Logs" as SupabaseLogs
}

Dev --> Repo : push / pull request
Repo --> Pipeline : dispara workflow
Pipeline --> Pipeline : instala dependencias\nejecuta pruebas y build
Pipeline --> Hosting : despliega version aprobada
Pipeline --> VercelLogs : registra resultado\nde despliegue

Usuario --> Internet : accede a URL publica
Internet --> CDN : HTTPS
CDN --> Hosting : entrega frontend
Hosting --> NextApp : renderiza rutas
NextApp --> ServerlessAPI : invoca operaciones seguras

ServerlessAPI --> SupabaseAuth : login, sesion y roles
ServerlessAPI --> SupabaseDB : vendedores, puestos,\nlicencias, inspecciones,\nreportes y panel
ServerlessAPI --> SupabaseStorage : evidencias de reportes\ne inspecciones

NextApp --> VercelLogs : errores de cliente\ny rendimiento
ServerlessAPI --> VercelLogs : logs de API
SupabaseAuth --> SupabaseLogs : eventos de autenticacion
SupabaseDB --> SupabaseLogs : consultas y errores
SupabaseStorage --> SupabaseLogs : eventos de archivos

note right of CDN
  La red Edge/CDN acerca la aplicacion
  a los usuarios y mejora el tiempo de carga.
end note

note bottom of Pipeline
  El flujo CI/CD automatiza validacion y despliegue
  para mantener una version publica estable.
end note

@enduml
